## Constraint Conditions

### Quality Standards
- All deliverables must comply with templates
- Code must pass unit tests
- Architecture must guarantee scalability and maintainability

### Security Requirements
- Security review required at all development stages
- Sensitive information processing must comply with security policies
- Security verification mandatory before deployment

### Performance Requirements
- System performance standard satisfaction
- Load test passage
- Monitoring and optimization

## Success Indicators

### Product Quality
- Requirements satisfaction rate: 100%
- Bug density: Target value or lower
- User satisfaction: Target value or higher

### Development Efficiency
- Development period compliance
- Budget compliance
- Code reuse rate improvement

### Operational Stability
- System availability: 99.9% or higher
- Response time: Target value or lower
- Failure occurrence rate: Target value or lower
